In case you missed it, here are the top News stories of the week: 1. GOGO (64): BEN 10 is my soulmate For the last 22 years, gogo Thelma "Nteng-Nteng" Mabuto (64) has been with her Ben 10. 2. 'Kelly SHOT Senzo!' "I put it to you that... an eyewitness will testify that Senzo Robert Meyiwa was allegedly shot by Nonhlanhla Kelly Khumalo by mistake." 3. UMSHADO ends in flames! For 19 glorious years, Hlengani Mabasa and his wife lived happily together. But then she started suspecting that he was cheating on her and that was never part of the deal. 4. 'Senzo was shot by mistake' The explosive comment came during cross examination by defence lawyer Advocate Malesela Teffo. 5. WATCH: Madala moered by Mboro's people The elders were called to investigate the loud noise coming from a powerful sound system in the neighbourhood.